        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 27. Calcareous rings. a–c: Phyrella fragilis (a: UF 4096, b: WAM Z26012, c: WAM Z26013); d–e: Phyrella trapeza, syntypes (d: MCZ HOL1488, thick body wall; e: MCZ HOL1488, thin body wall); f: Phyrella thyonoides, holotype (MCZ HOL1654); g: Phyrella cf. thyonoides (UF 9601); h: Phyrella mookiei, paratype (UF 4770); i: Phyllophorus aculeatus, holotype (USNM 1871)." ;
