        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 2. Ossicle assemblage of Phyrella trapeza (MCZ HOL1488, thick body wall). a–h: tables (a–f) and perforated plates (g–h) from mid-dorsal body wall; i–o: tables (i–m) and perforated plates (n–o) from mid-ventral body wall; p–v: tables (q–r) and perforated plates (s–v) from introvert; w–z; A–C: tables (w–z, A) and perforated plates (B–C) from cloacal region; D–E: rods from tentacles." ;
